<plot>Moments explores how the search for truth can be as fruitless as it may be enlightening. It's a story about the gauntlet of human experience: sadness, anger, joy and despair - and how people's life experiences often mirror each other. At its essence, this is a film that is about the search for truth in one's life through the evaluation of the most basic experience: moments.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?015916</url></doc>
